snippet.title: Oakwood Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Oakwood, a long abandoned campground nestled in the forests of British Columbia. Explore the woods, caves and dilapidated lodge in search of your friends, while surviving the prehistoric horrors that now haunt the grounds.

Available on Steam December 4th, 2018 https://store.steampowered.com/app/890970/Oakwood/
